\ip \bd ?Pah t…ôm…ôte naoa u?\bd* Aposol Jon t…ôm…ôte naoa u. In pia Jemes, k…ôn ilau n…ôt…® Sepeti mil. In net…ôm tuelef kit r…ôha Iesu, k…ôn Iesu tolkeike p…®k in. In t…ôm…ôte naoa m…®n u: Namnus…ôn T…ôw…®r it…ôm Jon T…ôm…ôte, 1 Jon, 2 Jon, 3 Jon, ne Nol ∆èp…ôn.  
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte tatuw…®n k…ôm pah?\bd* In t…ôm…ôte naoa u tatuw…®n k…ôm nim…ôfak sep…®n it…ôm koatat…®g e n…®t…ôn m…®n ik…®n Esia, ne matuw…®n m…®n k…ôm nim…ôfak m…®n ik…®n m…®n rafin.  
\ip \bd ?N…ômeg…ôh…ôn tahro nulan nian t…ôm…ôte?\bd* Nian u it…ôm t…ôm…ôte naoa lan, kapman r…ôha Rom t…ôm…ôn m…ôm…ô net…ômim okot…ôk…ôike mot…ôfak k…ôm et…ôm-iasol r…ôha kapman tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô in uhg…®n r…ôhalat. M…ôto net…ôm r…ôha nim…ôfak kot…ôm…ô et…ômim kiti…ôh …ôm in il…®s ag…®n, et…ômim u in Iesu Kristo. In …ôm un, in I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô. Tol n…ôhlan, kapman r…ôha Rom t…®natol n…ôrat…ôn k…ôm i…ôfak m…®n. K…ômotahl-ip…ôn Jon tuw…®n is…ôu e n…ôpt…ôn kit u, kat…ôn m…ôm…ô Patmos m…ôm…ô ot…ôtat…®g in p…®s…®n …ôm. Uhg…®n tos-ip…ôn nap…®laiir…ôn w…®r ag…®n kit k…ôm Jon m…ôm…ô ot…ôplan Iesu Kristo …ôp…ôh e nego e neai. K…ôn in m…ôplan m…®n nat…®mnat it…ôm ot…ôpanuwa, tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô inu: nol…ôn it…ôm Uhg…®n otol win e n…ôluag…®n…ôn it…ôm net…ômim ne Setan okotol ilat min, ne nol…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n o nakil…ôn net…ômim e namnun nian.  
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte naoa u o naka?\bd* In t…ôm…ôte naoa u m…ôm…ô otol …ôp m…ôm…ô Iesu Kristo in I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, k…ônu m…ôg…ôtun r…ôhan n…ôsan…ôn…ôn. K…ôn in tolkeike m…ôm…ô ot…ôn k…ôm i…ôfak m…®n m…ôm…ô okot…ôtul …ôskas…®k ok…ôm…ô nian i…ôk…®s m…®n okotuwa, k…ônu ilat ok…ôsot…ôfak…ôn k…ôm et…ôm-iasol r…ôha Rom m…ôm…ô in Uhg…®n. Ot…ôsuw…ôh…ôn, k…ônu Setan tol n…ôrat…ôn k…ôm i…ôfak m…®n, m…ôto ilat okot…ôk…ôike mot…ôtul …ôskas…®k, k…ôn in tolkeike m…ôm…ô ot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôha i…ôfak m…®n ne net…ômim u ilat koatat…®g e nian i…ôk…®s m…®n nian u roiu. Nian Iesu Kristo ot…®t…ôl…®g-pa m…®n, k…ôn in ot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr ilat.  
\c 1  
\s1 N…ôtuoun…ôn n…ôghat…ôn  
\m
\v 1 Naoa u, in tat…ôghat-in nat…®mnat m…®n it…ôm Iesu Kristo t…ômol …ôp.\f + \fr 1:1 \ft ‚ÄúT…ômol …ôp,‚Äù n…®p…ôt…®n u, m…ôm…ô tat…ôg…ôtun nat kit it…ôm aup…ôn, n…®p…ôt…®n tat…ôhluaig. E Bislama, kat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äúrivilem.‚Äù\f* Nat…®mnat m…®n u, Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…ôn k…ôm Iesu, m…ôm…ô in ot…ôg…ôtun k…ôm r…ôhan iolw…ôk m…®n nat…®mnat it…ôm ot…ôsuw…ôh…ôn t…ôike muwa. Kristo t…ômahl-ip…ôn r…ôhan kit nagelo tuwa, k…ôn m…ôg…ôtun nat…®mnat m…®n u k…ôm r…ôhan iolw…ôk, Jon.  
\v 2 Jon t…ôm…ôtul-ar…ôp o nat…®mnat rafin it…ôm in t…ôm…ôplan, k…ôn m…ôte r…ôk…®s ilat e naoa u. Nat…®mnat m…®n un it…ôm in t…ôm…ôplan, in n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n ne n…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn r…ôha Iesu Kristo.  
\v 3 Et…ôm un it…ôm t…ôtafin-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn m…®n u, it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômos-ipa, in otat…®g e n…ôw…®r…ôn pahrien. K…ôn net…ôm m…®n un it…ôm koat…ôto k…ôn moatos e n…®kilat k…ôn moatol, okotat…®g m…®n e n…ôw…®r…ôn pahrien, m…ôto-inu nian r…ôha nat…®mnat m…®n u, naoa u tat…ôghat-in, t…®n…ôku…ôk…®r ag…®n.   
\s1 Jon t…ôm…ôte naoa k…ôm nim…ôfak m…®n ilat sep…®n  
\p
\v 4 Io Jon, etahl-ip…ôn naoa u tatuw…®n k…ôm nim…ôfak m…®n ilat sep…®n …ôp…ôh e n…®t…ôn Esia.  
\p P…ôs Uhg…®n u it…ôm t…ôtat…®g roiu, t…ôm…ôtat…®g lil…®n, k…ôn ot…ôpanat…®g lil…®n m…®n, in otawte-in r…ôhan n…ôw…®r…ôn ne n…ôm…ôlinu…ôn k…ôm it…ômat. K…ôn p…ôs narm…®n ilat sep…®n\f + \fr 1:4 \ft Narm…®n ilat sep…®n it…ôm koatat…®g aup…ôn e r…ôhan t…®ron, (Nol ∆èp…ôn 3:1; 4:4; 5:6), ok…ôm-naka in suat…®p r…ôha n…ôn…ôn Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n; m…ôto ok…ôm-naka ilat nagelo sep…®n u kot…ôsan…ôn (Nol ∆èp…ôn 1:20; 8:2) it…ôm koatat…®g aup…ôn e t…®ron. Nampa sep…®n u, k…ômehm mau fifti-foa e Nol ∆èp…ôn. E Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n, nian neen tat…ôn ‚Äúilat sep…®n‚Äù m…ôto n…®p…ôt…®n m…ôm…ô ilat rafin ag…®n.\f* it…ôm koatat…®g aup…ôn e jea r…ôha kig, ilat m…®n okotol nulan et…ômat.  
\v 5 K…ôn Iesu Kristo m…®n, in otawte-in m…®n nulan k…ôm it…ômat. Kristo un t…ôm…ôtul-ar…ôp …ôskas…®k o n…®pahrien…ôn, k…ônu in…ôh, in et…ômim it…ôm in t…ômaup…ôn m…ômeg…ôh lil…®n e n…®m…®s…ôn,\f + \fr 1:5 \ft Kol 1:18; Sam 89:27\f* k…ôn in t…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô e kig m…®n r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn.\f + \fr 1:5 \ft Sam 89:27; Nol ∆èp…ôn 17:14; 19:16\f*  
\p P…ôs n…ônwiwi…ôn tuw…®n o Iesu Kristo u, in t…ômolkeike itat, k…ôn n…®tan t…ômai…ôh m…ôm…ô ot…®k…®s itat e nol…ôn r…ôha t…ôfag…ô rat.  
\v 6 In Kig r…ôhatat, k…ôn t…ômol kitat kotat…®g ahgin r…ôhan n…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn, k…ôn mol kitat kotuwa pris m…®n r…ôha Uhg…®n r…ôhan, koatol w…ôk r…ôha Tata r…ôhan. !P…ôs n…ônwiwi…ôn o r…ôhan nep…ôt…ôn ne n…ôsan…ôn…ôn tuw…®n o Iesu Kristo, namnun t…®k…ô! !P…ôs in ot…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô lil…®n! P…ôs otol n…ôhlan. ∆èw…ôh.   
\p
\v 7 !Ot…ôplan-tu! In tatuwa e mal napu…ô,\f + \fr 1:7 \ft Dan 7:13\f* k…ôn net…ômim rafin okot…ôtag-p…ôn mot…ôplan e n…®gan…ômt…®lat …ôtuat…®p, k…ôn net…ôm m…®n u k…ômotaru in aup…ôn, okot…ôplan m…®n, k…ôn netemim e noanol m…®n rafin e n…ôtueint…ôn, n…®kilat otahm…ô, motas…ôk …ôf…ôm…ôh m…ôto-inu k…ômot…ôplan.\f + \fr 1:7 \ft Sek 12:10\f*  
\p In ot…ôk…ôike mol n…ôhlan. !∆èw…ôh!   
\p
\v 8 I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Uhg…®n tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIo N…ôuk…ôt…®n ne Namnun.\f + \fr 1:8 \ft N…ôghat…ôn …ôtuat…®p u r…ôha Iesu, ‚ÄúIo un, Alfa ne Omeka.‚Äù Alfa un, in leta tat…ôtul aup…ôn e alfabet r…ôha n…ôghat…ôn Kris, k…ôn Omeka un, in leta it…ôm tatol namnun lan, tahmen e A ne Z e Inglis.\f* Io u etat…®g roiu, k…ôn em…ôtat…®g lil…®n, k…ôn epan…ôtat…®g lil…®n m…®n, k…ôn io un, Nahgik Tep…ôt P…®k Ag…®n.‚Äù   
\s1 Jon t…ôm…ôplan N…ôt…® Et…ômim  
\p
\v 9 Io Jon, piat…ômat u, it…ôm kitat koatos k…ôl…ôh nelm…®tat m…®n kiti…ôh e Iesu o nahm…ô…ôn, ne nat…®g…ôn e n…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn r…ôhan, ne n…ôtul …ôskas…®k…ôn e nian r…ôha nahm…ô…ôn. K…ôm…ôrakin-p…ôn io e n…ôpt…ôn u Patmos,\f + \fr 1:9 \ft N…ôpt…ôn u Patmos, in aelan kit.\f* m…ôto-inun iat…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn m…®n un it…ôm Uhg…®n tatos-ipa, k…ôn mat…ôtul-ar…ôp o Iesu.\fig |alt="map of seven churches" src="TNN SevenChurches.ai" size="col" loc="Rev 1:20" ref="Nol ∆èp…ôn 1:9" \fig*  
\v 10 In Nian r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô r…ôhatat,\f + \fr 1:10 \ft Nian r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô u, in Santei.\f* k…ôn em…ôrioah e Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ôn r…ôhan n…ôsan…ôn…ôn t…ômol k…ôm io, k…ôn ek…ôto n…ôwian asol kit e m…ôntaak, tahmen …ôm e t…ôwi,  
\v 11 k…ôn n…ôwian u tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú∆ète r…ôk…®s e naoa nat…®mnat m…®n rafin it…ôm nat…ôplan k…ôn mahl-ip…ôn k…ôm nim…ôfak sep…®n. Ilat koatuw…®n k…ôm Efesas, k…ôn S…®mana, k…ôn Pekamam, k…ôn Tuatira, ne Satis, ne Filatelfia, ne Laotisia.‚Äù   
\p
\v 12 K…ôn …ômun, ekeirair m…ôm…ô ek…ôplan-tu, m…ôm…ô pah tat…ôghat k…ôm io. K…ôn nian emeirair, m…ôplan nat kat…ôhtu-p…ôr lait lan, ilat sep…®n, k…ômol e iaen u kol tat…®p…®t-…®p…®t,  
\v 13 k…ôn ilug…®n e nat kat…ôhtu-p…ôr lait m…®n u lan, em…ôplan suah kit tahmen e N…ôt…® Et…ômim,\f + \fr 1:13 \ft Dan 7:13\f* r…ôhan nap…ôn kaif…ôm…ôh u kaif…ôm…ôh. K…ôn k…ôm…ôlis man…®k…®l…ôhan e k…ôt…ôut, k…ômol e iaen u kol tat…®p…®t-…®p…®t.\f + \fr 1:13 \ft Nap…ôn …ôh kat…ôn, in nap…ôn r…ôha pris asol ag…®n. Iesu in r…ôhatat pris asol ag…®n.\f*  
\v 14 R…ôhn-kap…ô ne noanun t…ôru…ôn t…ôru…ôn m…ô nahwi noan n…®t…ôh…ôi,\f + \fr 1:14 \ft N…ôghat…ôn Kris …ôtuat…®p tat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äúin t…ôru…ôn t…ôru…ôn m…ô sno.‚Äù\f* \f + \fr 1:14 \ft Dan 7:9\f* k…ôn n…®gan…ômt…®n t…ôtasi…ô tahmen e n…ômnam…®n n…®g…ôm.\f + \fr 1:14 \ft Esik 1:28\f*  
\v 15 Nelk…®n tahmen e p…®rons,\f + \fr 1:15 \ft P…®rons, in iaen kit, kala r…ôhan tahmen e kol.\f* it…ôm k…ômaan e n…®g…ôm m…ôm…ô otai…ôh r…ôk…®s-in namt…ô…ôn, maf…ôl it…ôm t…ôw…®r, k…ôn uaris…®g un, k…ôr…ôpe m…ôm…ô in ot…ôw…®r mat…®p…®t-…®p…®t. K…ôn n…ôwian iahgin iahgin tahmen e n…®t…ôh…ôi asol kit tatem noanahlu…ôlu…ô;  
\v 16 In tatos m…ôhau ilat sep…®n e nelm…®n mat…®p, k…ônu naip kit r…ôha n…ôluag…®n…ôn in tas…®l…ô e n…®kal…®n k…ôr…ôn mil,\f + \fr 1:16 \ft Hip 4:12; Jon 12:48\f* tat…®s…®-p…ôn e n…®p…ôgnoan, k…ôn suah un t…ôhag-…ôhag m…®tasi…ô, tahmen e m…®tgar …ôp…ô e n…ôraui…ôg…ôn.   
\p
\v 17 Nian em…ôplan suah …ôh, emeiuaiu morin io …ôh nelk…®n ik…®n, tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô em…®m…®s.\f + \fr 1:17 \ft Dan 8:17; 10:15; Mat 17:6\f* M…ôto in t…ômea-pa mek io e r…ôhn mat…®p k…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú∆ès…ôg…®n…ôn. Io u, io emaup…ôn mat…®g, k…ôn io iatol namnun ag…®n.  
\v 18 Io u, Et…ôm Tat…ômeg…ôh.\f + \fr 1:18 \ft Sam 42:2\f* !Em…®m…®s aup…ôn, k…ôn m…ôto …ôplan-tu, iat…ômeg…ôh lil…®n! K…ôn io iatos ki r…ôha N…®m…®s…ôn ne ki r…ôha Noanp…ôn.\f + \fr 1:18 \ft ‚ÄúIo iatos ki r…ôha N…®m…®s…ôn ne ki r…ôha Noanp…ôn,‚Äù n…®p…ôt…®n u m…ôm…ô iatos nep…ôt…ôn o nahtos…®g…ôn ne ner…ôh…ôn e ket r…ôha Im…ô Net…ôm K…ômot…®m…®s Ik…®n, k…ôn mol net…ômim k…ômot…®m…®s ilat kot…ômeg…ôh m…®n.\f*   
\p
\v 19 ‚ÄúTol n…ôhlan, …ôte r…ôk…®s nat naka it…ôm n…ôm…ôplan, k…ôn neen nat…ôplan u-roiu, ne nat…®mnat neen m…®n it…ôm tatuwa.  
\v 20 M…ôto ekuhap…®k e n…®p…ôt…® m…ôhau m…®n ilat sep…®n it…ôm n…ôm…ôplan iatos e nelm…ôk mat…®p, ne nat kat…ôhtu-p…ôr lait lan, ilat sep…®n, k…ômol e iaen u kol tat…®p…®t-…®p…®t. M…ôhau m…®n u ilat sep…®n, n…®p…ôt…®n u nagelo m…®n r…ôha nim…ôfak sep…®n. K…ônu nat kat…ôhtu-p…ôr lait lan, ilat sep…®n, k…ômol e kol, n…®p…ôt…®n un, nim…ôfak m…®n un ilat sep…®n.   
\c 2  
\s1 N…ôghat…ôn t…ômuw…®n k…ôm i…ôfak m…®n ik…®n Efesas  
