\v 4 M…ôto iatehm n…®p…ôgn…ômt…®n kit …ôh-ik…®n n…ômotol, t…ôsahmen…ôn e n…®gan…ômt…ôk. N…ômotap…ôs nolkeike…ôn\f + \fr 2:4 \ft Jon 13:35; Jer 2:2-5\f* aup…ôn r…ôhat…ômat.  
\v 5 N…®kit…ômat tu…ôh-tu nolkeike…ôn it…ôm n…ômoatat…®g lan aup…ôn. Ot…ôuhlin it…ômat, k…ôn motol nat…®mnat m…®n u n…ômoatol aup…ôn. Ok…ôm…ô n…ôsotol…ôn, k…ôn ekuwa, m…®l…ôs-ir…ôk…®s r…ôhat…ômat nat kat…ôhtu-p…ôr lait lan e n…ômeen.  
\v 6 M…ôto nat kiti…ôh …ôm …ôh-ik…®n, noatol in t…ôw…®r. It…ômat nakotet…ôhau nol…ôn rat m…®n r…ôha net…ômim r…ôha Nikolas,\f + \fr 2:6 \ft Net…ôm r…ôha Nikolas m…®n un, kitat k…ôsot…®tun w…®r…ôn nat…®mnat tep…ôt elat o r…ôhalat et…ôm-iasol. Ilat net…ômim neen r…ôha nim…ôfak, m…ôto ilat koat…ôn m…ôm…ô k…®tun n…ôfak…ôn k…ôm narm…® nat m…®n, k…ônu k…®tun nit …ôpnap…®n…ôn it…ôm. Ilat koat…ôn m…ôm…ô nol…ôn m…®n …ôh, t…ôs…ôr…ôk…®n…ôn narm…®t…ôm.\f* tahmen …ôm lak, iatol mihin.   
