\v 7 Et…ôm mat…ôlg…®n tat…®g, in ot…ôk…ôike m…ôt…ôl…®g-in w…®r n…ôghat…ôn m…®n it…ôm Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n tat…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm nim…ôfak m…®n. Et…ôm otol win e n…ôluag…®n…ôn u, io iateg…ôhan-in m…ôm…ô in otun noa n…®g r…ôha n…ômeg…ôh…ôn it…ôm tat…ôwi…ô e nasum…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n.‚Äù\f + \fr 2:7 \ft Jen 2:9; 3:22-24; Rom 5:12,18; 6:23; Nol ∆èp…ôn 22:2\f*   
\s1 N…ôghat…ôn t…ômuw…®n k…ôm i…ôfak m…®n ik…®n S…®mana  
