\v 12 Et…ôm otol win e n…ôluag…®n…ôn, k…ôn io oekol in tahmen e n…®g asol kit it…ôm t…ôtaru…ôsan Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n r…ôhak. K…ôn in okol t…ôsiet…ôn e Nim…ô …ôh nian kit. K…ôn io, oek…ôte-p…ôn n…ôrg…® Uhg…®n r…ôhak lan, ne n…ôrg…® taon r…ôha Uhg…®n r…ôhak lan. Taon u, in Jerusalem wi, it…ôm Uhg…®n r…ôhak otahl-ipa, ot…®s…®-p…ôr e nego e neai, meiuaiu-pa. K…ôn io oek…ôte-p…ôn m…®n n…ôrg…ôk wi e suah u.   
