\v 5 K…ôn et…ôm-iasol m…®n u kit it…ôm t…ôm…ôwi…ôt…ôn, t…ôn-ipa k…ôm io m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!Sas…ôk…ôn! M…®tag-p…ôn-tu m…ôplan, Laion r…ôha Noanol r…ôha Juta,\f + \fr 5:5 \ft Jen 49:9-10\f* in n…ôuk…ôt…® Tef…®t,\f + \fr 5:5 \ft Aes 11:1\f* in t…®nol win r…ôk…®s e n…ôluag…®n…ôn r…ôhan. Tol n…ôhlan, in t…ôtuat…®p ag…®n-…ôh o nurap…®k…ôn naoa …ôh, k…ôn meat…®p r…ôk…®s nat …ôh ilat sep…®n it…ôm k…ômuwaan …ôtain lan.‚Äù   
