\v 12 moat…ôn m…ôm…ô:  
\q1 ‚Äú!∆èw…ôh! !N…®pahrien…ôn! R…ôhatat Uhg…®n t…ôw…®r p…®k, mat…ôhag-…ôhag w…®r.  
