\p
\v 17 K…ôn …ômun ek…ôtag-p…ôn m…ôplan nagelo kit tat…ôtul-p…ôn e m…®tgar, in t…ôtas…ôk …ôf…ôm…ôh mat…ôn-ip…ôn k…ôm m…ôn…®g m…®n it…ôm koatiw…®g …ôp…ôh e magoag…ôp, m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúOtuwa, motarg…ôtain it…ômat m…®n o nagw…ôn…ôn asol r…ôha Uhg…®n,  
\v 18 m…ôm…ô it…ômat on…ôkoton noanuw…ôhg…® kig m…®n, ne net…ôm-iasol r…ôha mopael m…®n, ne net…ôm nahgilat tep…ôt, ne hos m…®n, ne net…ôm koatasu…ô-p…ôr elat, ne noanuw…ôhg…® net…ômim rafin, net…ôm s…ôn…ôm…ô slef, ne slef m…®n, net…ôm koatos nep…ôt…ôn asol m…®n, ne net…ôm …ôpnap…®n …ôm.‚Äù   
\p
\v 19 K…ôn …ômun, ekat…®g m…ôplan m…®n nat meg…ôh …ôp…ôl…ô in, ne kig m…®n r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn ne r…ôhalat mopael m…®n. Ilat k…ômotarg…ôtain ilat m…®n m…ôm…ô okot…ôluag…®n ilat et…ôm t…®tasu…ô e hos k…ôru…ôn, ne r…ôhan mopael m…®n.  
\v 20 M…ôto k…ômotask…ôl…®m nat meg…ôh …ôh, ne ien eiu…ô-eiu…ô it…ôm t…ômatol n…ômt…ôtin p…®sp…®s m…®n nian t…ôm…ôtat…®g ilau nat meg…ôh. In t…ômatol n…ômt…ôtin m…®n …ôh, o neiu…ô-in…ôn net…ôm m…®n u it…ôm koatos mak r…ôha nat meg…ôh, k…ôn mot…ôfak k…ôm narm…®n it…ôm k…ômasg…ôw…®n e n…®g. K…ômot…ôrakin-p…ôn ilau k…ôr…ôn katu…ômeg…ôh …ôm, …ôp…ôh e n…®p…ôgnoa n…ômnam…®n n…®g…ôm asol it…ôm t…ôg…ôpan matu…ôp mat…ôpien.  
\v 21 Et…ôm t…®tatasu…ô e hos k…ôru…ôn, t…ômohamnu kig m…®n ne mopael m…®n rafin e naip r…ôha n…ôluag…®n…ôn it…ôm tat…®s…®-p…ôn e n…®p…ôgnoan k…ôn m…ôn…®g m…®n rafin k…ômoton n…®p…ôt…®lat, moton, n…ôrp…®lat tasis w…®r.   
\c 20  
\s1 Kristo t…ômuwa mol Kig k…ôn m…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô e net…ômim m…ôtoarus-p…ôn nup wan-taosen  
\m
\v 1 K…ôn …ômun, em…ôplan nagelo kit tat…®s…®-p…ôr e nego e neai, tatos ki r…ôha n…®p…ôg asol it…ôm teiuaiu ag…®n,\f + \fr 20:1 \ft Nol ∆èp…ôn 1:18\f* ne sen asol kit.  
\v 2 K…ôn in t…ômask…ôl…®m ialkita asol u, s…®nek nuw…ôh ilouin aup…ôn, in I…ôrm…®s, o Setan, k…ôn m…ôlis …ôtain o nup wan-taosen.  
\v 3 T…ôm…ôrakin-p…ôn in e n…®p…ôg asol it…ôm teiuaiu ag…®n, k…ôn mahtos…®g-in ti…ôk…®s, m…ôm…ô in ot…ôseiu…ô-in m…®n…ôn net…ômim r…ôha kantri m…®n m…ôtoarus-p…ôn nup wan-taosen tol namnun. Nup wan-taosen otol namnun un, ok…ôike ker…ôh m…®n lan o nian …ôku…ôk…®r m…®n …ôm.   
\p
\v 4 K…ôn …ômun, em…ôplan jea r…ôha kig m…®n neen, k…ôn net…ômim it…ôm koat…ôp…ôl…ôh-p…ôr elat. Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…ôn nep…ôt…ôn k…ôm ilat m…ôm…ô ilat okotakil net…ômim. K…ôn ek…ôplan m…®n net…ômim it…ôm k…ôm…ôtat…®p nentoulat m…ôto-inu k…ômot…ôtul-ar…ôp o n…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r r…ôha Iesu ne n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n. Ilat k…ôm…ôsot…ôfak…ôn k…ôm nat meg…ôh ne narm…®n it…ôm k…ômasg…ôw…®n e n…®g, k…ôn m…ôsotos…ôn r…ôhan mak e n…®p…®n…ôg…®lat ne nelm…®lat. K…ôn roiu ilat k…ômot…ômeg…ôh m…®n, k…ôn mot…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô ilat Kristo o nup wan-taosen.  
\v 5 Nat …ôh, in naiir-pa-m…®n…ôn e n…®m…®s…ôn it…ôm otaup…ôn. M…ôto net…ôm m…®n u neen m…®n it…ôm k…ômot…®m…®s r…ôk…®s, ilat k…ômotos mak r…ôha nat meg…ôh ilouin, k…ôm…ôsot…ômeg…ôh m…®n…ôn m…ôtoarus nup wan-taosen tol namnun.  
\v 6 Net…ôm m…®n un, it…ôm k…ômaup…ôn kos ilat e naiir-pa-m…®n…ôn e n…®m…®s…ôn, ilat okotat…®g e n…ôw…®r…ôn pahrien, m…ôto-inu ilat net…ôm asim m…®n r…ôha Uhg…®n. Ilat ok…ôsotuw…®n…ôn e noan…ômnam…®n n…®g…ôm asol, m…ôto ilat okotuwa motol pris m…®n r…ôha Uhg…®n ne r…ôha Kristo, k…ôn ilat okot…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô ilat min e nup wan-taosen.   
\s1 Uhg…®n t…ômol nalp…®n…ôn k…ôm Setan  
\p
\v 7 Nian nup wan-taosen t…®nol namnun, okahl-iar…ôp m…®n Setan e n…®p…ôg asol.  
\v 8 K…ôn in otuw…®n …ôp…ôh o net…ômim e kona kuw…®t r…ôha n…ôtueint…ôn, it…ôm kat…ôn m…ôm…ô Kok ne Makok,\f + \fr 20:8 \ft Esik 38:2,9,15\f* m…ôm…ô oteiu…ô-in ilat, k…ôn mos rafin ilat marg…ôtain ilat o n…ôluag…®n…ôn. Ilat rafin otep…ôt otep…ôt, nampa r…ôhalat in tahmen e n…®m…ôkl…ôk…®l …ôp…ôh e n…®kal…® it…ôh…ôi.  
\v 9 Ilat k…ômotaliw…ôk motuw…®n is…ôu is…ôu m…®n mot…®r…ôfin n…ôtueint…ôn. K…ôn ilat k…ômot…ôtul k…®t…ôlau-in ik…®n net…ômim r…ôha Uhg…®n okotat…®g ik…®n, ne taon asol u it…ôm Uhg…®n tolkeike p…®k.\f + \fr 20:9 \ft ‚ÄúTaon u, it…ôm Uhg…®n tolkeike p…®k,‚Äù in tat…ôghat-in Jerusalem.\f* M…ôto n…®g…ôm kit t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôr e nego e neai, muwa mus ilat.  
\v 10 K…ôn k…ôm…ôrakin-p…ôn I…ôrm…®s it…ôm t…ômatos-ip…ôn os-ip…ôn k…ôm ilat, k…ôm…ôrakin-p…ôn …ôp…ôh e noan…ômnam…®n n…®g…ôm asol it…ôm tat…ôpien. Ik…®n …ôh, k…ôm…ôrakin-p…ôn r…ôk…®s nat meg…ôh ne ien eiueiu…ô. Il…ôhal ok…ôt…ôhal…ôto nahm…ô…ôn lil…®n e n…ôraui…ôg…ôn ne lap…®n, namnun t…®k…ô.   
\s1 Namnun nakil…ôn  
\p
\v 11 K…ôn …ômun ek…ôplan m…®n jea asol kit, t…ôru…ôn. K…ôn kig tat…ôp…ôl…ôh-p…ôr lan. N…ôtueint…ôn ne neai k…ômuag…®m o n…®gan…ômt…®n, miak…ô ag…®n.   
\p
\v 12 K…ôn …ômun ek…ôplan net…ôm k…ômot…®m…®s, net…ôm koatos nep…ôt…ôn asol, ne net…ôm …ôpnap…®n …ôm. Ilat rafin kot…ôtul aup…ôn e jea r…ôha kig u, k…ôn kameg naoa m…®n.\f + \fr 20:12 \ft Nat…®mnat rafin it…ôm net…ômim k…ômotol, k…ôm…ôte r…ôk…®s e naoa m…®n u.\f* K…ôn kameg m…®n naoa kit, inu naoa r…ôha n…ômeg…ôh…ôn. Okehm nakil…ôn r…ôha net…ôm k…ômot…®m…®s e naoa m…®n u, k…ôn k…®natakil ilat kiti…ôh kiti…ôh o nat ilat k…ômotol.  
\v 13 N…ôrp…® n…®t…ôh…ôi t…ôm…ôhlman net…ôm k…ômot…®m…®s it…ôh…ôi, k…ôn N…®m…®s…ôn ne Noanp…ôn k…ômu…ôhlman m…®n ilat, ilat k…®notiet r…ôk…®s elau, k…ôn k…®natakil ilat kiti…ôh kiti…ôh o nat ilat k…ômotol.  
\v 14 K…ôn k…ôm…®l…ôs N…®m…®s…ôn ne Noanp…ôn, k…ôrakin-p…ôn ilau e noan…ômnam…®n n…®g…ôm asol. Noan…ômnam…®n n…®g…ôm asol u, in n…®m…®s…ôn mau k…ôiu.  
\v 15 Ok…ôm…ô k…ôsehm…ôn n…ôrg…® suah kit e naoa r…ôha n…ômeg…ôh…ôn, k…ôn ok…ôrakin-p…ôn in e noan…ômnam…®n n…®g…ôm asol.   
\c 21  
\s1 Jerusalem wi  
\m
\v 1 K…ôn …ômun em…ôplan neai wi ne n…ôtueint…ôn wi, m…ôto-inu neai oas ne n…ôtueint…ôn oas k…®niak…ô. K…ôn n…®t…ôh…ôi t…ôm…®k…ô m…®n.  
\v 2 K…ôn …ômun ek…ôplan taon asim r…ôha Uhg…®n, inun Jerusalem wi, tat…®s…®-p…ôr o Uhg…®n e nego e neai mateiuaiu-pa. K…ômol mal…ô-mal…ô lan tahmen e p…ôtan it…ôm k…ômol mal…ô-mal…ô k…ôm in m…ôm…ô otuw…®n mehm r…ôhan i…ôrman mioal mar…®t.  
\v 3 K…ôn …ômun ek…ôto n…ôwian asol kit t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôn …ôp…ôh e jea r…ôha kig mat…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!∆èplan-tu! Roiu …ôh, Uhg…®n t…®nol latu…ônu r…ôhan ilat net…ômim. In ot…ôtat…®g ilat min, k…ôn ilat okotuwa r…ôhan m…®n net…ômim. K…ôn Uhg…®n …ôtuat…®p in ot…ôtat…®g olat, k…ôn in r…ôhalat Uhg…®n.  
\v 4 In otaf…ôl r…ôk…®s rafin nahui n…ômt…®lat. N…®m…®s…ôn ne nas…ôk…ôn ne nahm…ô…ôn m…®n okot…®k…ô. Nat…®mnat nuw…ôh m…®n u, ilat k…®notuw…®n r…ôk…®s, okol k…ôsotuwa m…®n…ôn.‚Äù   
\p
\v 5 Kig it…ôm tat…ôp…ôl…ôh-p…ôr e r…ôhan jea, t…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIat…ôuhlin nat…®mnat m…®n rafin kotuwa motuwiwi.‚Äù K…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú∆ète r…ôk…®s nat…®mnat m…®n u, m…ôto-inu n…ôghat…ôn m…®n u, k…®tun nag…®le…ôn elat m…ôm…ô n…®pahrien…ôn.‚Äù   
\p
\v 6 K…ôn mat…®g m…ôn-ipa m…®n k…ôm io m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúK…®nol namnun nat…®mnat rafin. Io N…ôuk…ôt…®n ne Namnun.\f + \fr 21:6 \ft N…ôghat…ôn …ôtuat…®p u r…ôha Iesu, ‚ÄúIo un, Alfa ne Omeka.‚Äù Alfa un, in leta tat…ôtul aup…ôn e alfabet r…ôha n…ôghat…ôn Kris, k…ôn Omeka un, in leta it…ôm tatol namnun lan, tahmen e A ne Z e Inglis.\f* Io n…ôtuoun…ôn, k…ôn io iatol namnun lan. Net…ômim it…ôm koatoaoa, io ekos-ip…ôn n…ôhau k…ôm ilat, it…ôm okot…ôn…®m m…ôsotos-n…ômt…®n…ôn. K…ôn inun, n…ômt…® n…ôhau it…ôm tat…ôr matos-ip…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn lil…®n.\f + \fr 21:6 \ft Aes 55:1-2; Jon 4:10; 6:35; 7:37-39\f*  
\v 7 Et…ômim it…ôm otat…ôtul-i…ôk…®s mol win e n…ôluag…®n…ôn r…ôhan, io ekos-ip…ôn nat…®mnat it…ôm em…ôn-i…ôk…®s r…ôk…®s k…ôm in. Io ekuwa r…ôhan Uhg…®n, k…ôn in otuwa n…ôt…®k.  
\v 8 M…ôto net…ôm koat…ôgin it…ôm, m…ôsot…ôtul …ôskas…®k…ôn e r…ôhalat nahat…ôt…ô…ôn, ilat kotamk…®m…®k, k…ôn moatohamnu it…ôm, koatit anion …ôm ilat m…®n, moatol klefa, moat…ôm…®k n…ôr…®k, mot…ôfak k…ôm narm…® nat m…®n, ne ieiueiu…ô m…®n rafin, im…ôlat …ôtuat…®p un in noan…ômnam…®n n…®g…ôm asol, tat…ôpien ik…®n. Nat u, in nampa tu n…®m…®s…ôn.‚Äù   
\p
\v 9 K…ôn …ômun, nagelo aup…ôn u kit tat…ôghat k…ôm io. In nagelo sep…®n m…®n u kit it…ôm k…ômoat…ôm…®k pes…®n ilat sep…®n it…ôm kot…ôrioah e namnu nalp…®n…ôn ilat sep…®n it…ôm Uhg…®n otol k…ôm net…ômim. In t…ômuwa m…ôn-ipa k…ôm io m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúWa-tu, p…ôs iak…ôg…ôtun p…ôtan r…ôha N…ôt…® Sipsip k…ôm ik, it…ôm okioal mar…®t ilau min.‚Äù  
\v 10 K…ôn n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôha Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n t…ômol k…ôm io, …ômun nagelo tit-ir…ôk…®s io ekian …ôp…ôh e n…®tot asol kit, n…®tot un, in il…®s u il…®s. K…ôn in t…ôg…ôtun k…ôm io Taon Asim r…ôha Uhg…®n u, Jerusalem wi, it…ôm t…ôm…®s…®-p…ôr o Uhg…®n …ôp…ôh il…®s e nego e neai.  
\v 11 In t…ôhag-…ôhag e nep…ôt…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n. Tat…®p…®t-…®p…®t tahmen e k…ôpiel w…®r kit u tiaspa, it…ôm talien m…ô k…®las.  
